## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **finerenone Kerendia 2021** = first FDA non-steroidal MR antagonist DKD. FIDELIO-DKD + FIGARO-DKD pivotal. spironolactone + eplerenone 의 hyperkalemia + gynecomastia 부작용 회피. quantum-VQE 의 MR ligand-binding domain selectivity 가 직접 fit.
2. **SGLT2i CKD label cascade 2019-2023** — CREDENCE (canagliflozin DKD 2019) + DAPA-CKD (dapagliflozin 2020) + EMPA-KIDNEY (empagliflozin 2022) = 만성 단백뇨 + non-DM CKD 까지 적응증 확장. 30+ years RAAS-only era 종료. quantum-VQE 의 SGLT2 transmembrane 결합 fit.
3. **vadadustat Vafseo 2022 + daprodustat Jesduvroq 2023** = first + second FDA HIF-PHI 만성 anemia of CKD. ESA (epoetin + darbepoetin) 의 oral alternative. PHD2 활성부위 + Fe(II) + 2-OG 결합 quantum-VQE 직접 fit. roxadustat (Evrenzo) US 미승인 + EU/한국/일본 허가 = regulatory divergence.
4. **tenapanor Xphozah 2023** = first FDA NHE3 inhibitor hyperphosphatemia CKD-D. luminal-restricted (no systemic absorption) 작은 분자 = phosphate 결합제 와 mechanism 다름 (paracellular permeability 차단). quantum-VQE 의 transmembrane NHE3 fit.
5. **patiromer Veltassa 2015 + Lokelma 2018** = first FDA hyperkalemia chronic. Kayexalate (SPS) classical 의 GI necrosis 부작용 vs Zr selective. RAAS + finerenone 병용시 hyperkalemia 관리 (cross-emergency_medicine).
6. **sparsentan Filspari 2023** = first FDA dual ETA + AT1 — IgAN 1차 적응증. CKD specific cross-link distinct (`.roadmap.disease_iga_nephropathy_specific`). DKD investigational.
7. **GLP-1 RA semaglutide FLOW 2024** = Ozempic + Rybelsus CKD label 추가. SGLT2i + GLP-1 RA + finerenone + RAAS = "quadruple therapy" DKD framework. quantum-VQE 의 GLP-1R + GIPR 결합 cross-metabolic.
8. **만성 transplant tacrolimus + MMF + steroid + everolimus + belatacept** = ESRD transplant immunosuppression. 만성 calcineurin inhibitor 신독성 paradox + 만성 mTOR + 만성 costimulation blockade trade-off (cross-transplant).
9. **한국 K-CKD + 식약처 + 보험 산정특례** — 만성 신질환 + 만성 dialysis 100% 환자 부담. K-DIGO + KCKD-CRC 임상 framework. 한국 ESRD 신환 발생 + 당뇨 신증 + 고혈압 신증 비중 증가.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, CKD + DKD + ESRD 임상 의미 한정. quantum-VQE 의 SGLT2 + MR + HIF-PHI + ENaC + ETA + NHE3 + CaSR 결합 = 6+ membrane target 동시.

